Atlanta Reign's Dafran
data.description: Meet Daniel “dafran” Francesca, famous streamer and DPS for the Atlanta Reign. Dafran talks about his rise to Overwatch stardom and his hopes for the 2019 season.

data.description: After falling short of the Inaugural Season playoffs, the Dallas Fuel had to rebuild from the ground up…literally. Check out Dallas Fuel’s new practice facility where they’ve replicated every detail from the Blizzard Arena to fuel the Fuel this season.
